### COMPILATION ###

To compile, use:

make

### EXECUTION ###

To execute a code line, use:

./bin/simulator -f architecture_file -t number_threads

### SOFTWARE MAN ###

You can find man pages in the folder cassis/man.

How to use the software:
cassis/documentation/man/cassis.1

How to use the architecture description files:
cassis/documentation/man/cassis-xml.1

### PACKAGES ###

xml packages needed:
libxml2-dev
libxslt1-dev

documentation packages needed:
doxygen
graphviz

lua package needed:
liblua5.2-0
liblua5.2-dev
